773
00:50:40,577 --> 00:50:42,540
You wouldn't know
what happened to him, would you?

774
00:50:43,338 --> 00:50:44,876
He was taken at my command

775
00:50:45,736 --> 00:50:46,961
to answer for his crimes.

776
00:50:50,751 --> 00:50:52,456
I'll bring the City Watch.

777
00:50:54,681 --> 00:50:55,703
Come, Stark.

778
00:50:56,673 --> 00:50:58,473
I'd rather you die sword in hand.

779
00:50:58,598 --> 00:51:00,442
- If you threaten My Lord again...
- Threaten?

780
00:51:00,777 --> 00:51:01,778
As in,

781
00:51:02,283 --> 00:51:04,674
"I'm going to open your lord
from balls to brains

782
00:51:04,799 --> 00:51:06,481
"and see what Starks are made of"?

783
00:51:07,585 --> 00:51:08,653
You kill me,

784
00:51:10,393 --> 00:51:11,859
your brother's a dead man.

785
00:51:12,837 --> 00:51:13,849
You're right.

786
00:51:14,629 --> 00:51:16,324
Take him alive.
Kill his men.

787
00:52:52,494 --> 00:52:55,361
My brother, Lord Stark...
We want him back.

